title: Manager button missing in team ranked
body: Hi, Don't know if anyone else is getting this problem but the manager button to add team players or remove them is missing... I'm the leader and cant even leave the team to make some one else captain. So if anyone knows how to fix this it would be greatly appreciated.

replies.body: The profile tab was recently reworked, so this might be a bit of collateral damage from that. Report the bug in [the appropriate board](http://boards.na.leagueoflegends.com/en/c/bug-report).
